### 1) Buscar TODOS os alunos
GET http://localhost:5000/alunos
Accept: application/json

###

### 2) Buscar aluno específico por ID (Ex: ID 1)
GET http://localhost:5000/alunos/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 3) Criar um novo aluno (POST)
POST http://localhost:5000/alunos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao@email.com"
}

###

### 4) Atualizar aluno completamente (PUT)
PUT http://localhost:5000/alunos/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "João da Silva",
  "email": "joao.silva@email.com",
  "telefone": "11999999999"
}

###

### 5) Atualizar aluno parcialmente (PATCH)
PATCH http://localhost:5000/alunos/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "telefone": "11888888888"
}

###

### 6) Deletar um aluno por ID
DELETE http://localhost:5000/alunos/1
